(3, 6, 'What is cloud computing primarily about?', 'Utilizing local servers for data storage', 'Accessing data offline', 'Using remote servers on the internet for data storage and access', ' None of the above', 'Using remote servers on the internet for data storage and access', 'Active', '2024-02-29 09:59:33'),
(4, 6, 'Which of the following operations can be performed using cloud computing?', ' Sending physical documents', ' Hosting websites', 'Operating only on local drives', 'None of the above', ' Hosting websites', 'Active', '2024-02-29 10:00:57'),
(5, 6, 'What was the traditional approach of IT companies before the emergence of cloud computing?', 'Relying solely on cloud services', 'Establishing extensive IT infrastructure', 'Outsourcing all IT operations', 'None of the above', 'Establishing extensive IT infrastructure', 'Active', '2024-02-29 10:01:44'),
(6, 6, 'Which characteristic of cloud computing allows users to access systems from any location or device?', 'Device and Location Independence', 'High Scalability', 'Maintenance', 'Low Cost', 'Device and Location Independence', 'Active', '2024-02-29 10:05:47'),
(8, 6, 'How are cloud computing applications maintained?', ' Through frequent hardware upgrades', 'By installing software on each users computer', 'They are easier to maintain compared to traditional applications', ' None of the above', 'They are easier to maintain compared to traditional applications', 'Active', '2024-02-29 10:20:09'),
(9, 6, 'How does cloud computing help in cost reduction?', 'By increasing hardware expenses', 'By eliminating the need for infrastructure establishment', 'By increasing software licensing fees', 'None of the above', 'By eliminating the need for infrastructure establishment', 'Active', '2024-02-29 10:24:51'),
(10, 6, 'How do users access cloud services', 'Through physical access to servers', 'Via provided APIs and paying charges based on usage', 'Through manual configuration of servers', 'None of the above', 'Via provided APIs and paying charges based on usage', 'Active', '2024-02-29 10:25:38'),
(11, 6, 'What advantage of cloud computing facilitates easy backup and restoration processes?', 'Enhanced Collaboration', 'Accessibility', 'Data Back-up and Restoration', 'Cost Savings', 'Data Back-up and Restoration', 'Active', '2024-02-29 10:29:01'),
(12, 6, 'How does cloud computing promote improved collaboration?', 'By offering mobility solutions', 'Through a pay-per-use model', 'By providing scalable storage', 'By enabling seamless information sharing through shared storage', 'By enabling seamless information sharing through shared storage', 'Active', '2024-02-29 10:30:12'),
(13, 6, 'Which advantage of cloud computing ensures quick and convenient access to stored information worldwide?', 'Mobility', 'Cost Savings', 'Enhanced Collaboration', 'Accessibility', 'Accessibility', 'Active', '2024-02-29 10:31:20'),
(14, 6, 'How does cloud computing contribute to cost savings?', 'By limiting control over services', 'Through vendor lock-in', 'By reducing hardware and software maintenance costs', 'By offering scalable storage', 'By reducing hardware and software maintenance costs', 'Active', '2024-02-29 10:32:10'),
(15, 6, 'What is a notable disadvantage of cloud computing concerning data access?', 'Limited Control', 'Security Concerns', 'Internet Dependency', 'Scalable Storage', 'Internet Dependency', 'Active', '2024-02-29 10:36:25'),
(16, 6, 'What makes transitioning services between different cloud vendors difficult?', 'Limited Control', 'Security Concerns', 'Internet Dependency', 'Vendor Lock-in', 'Vendor Lock-in', 'Active', '2024-02-29 10:41:39'),
(17, 6, 'What aspect of cloud infrastructure management limits users control?', 'Data Security', 'Limited Control', 'Vendor Lock-in', 'Security Concerns', 'Limited Control', 'Active', '2024-02-29 10:43:02'),
(18, 6, 'What is a significant security concern associated with cloud computing?', 'Internet Dependency', 'Limited Control', 'Vendor Lock-in', 'Security Concerns', 'Security Concerns', 'Active', '2024-02-29 10:43:53'),
