(20, 6, 'What was the computing paradigm that preceded cloud computing?', 'Mainframe Computing', 'Distributed Computing', 'Client-Server Computing', 'Personal Computing', 'Distributed Computing', 'Active', '2024-02-29 10:52:37'),
